svg.text: The era of the new “green gold”

Avocado is today the absolute star of Instagram posts and healthy diets. It entered the commercial market in the 90s as once a exotic tropical fruit, and in 2017 more than 135 millions kilos of avocado were consumed in the occasion of the Super Bowl week. In the same year’s summer the price of the so-called ‘green gold’ reached its peak, after a fast but constant growth, a sign of its rising economic and commercial value.
